==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: gōng qí wú bèi, chū qí bú yì
===Etymology===
*From: ''[[w:The Art of War|The Art of War]]'', by [[w:Sunzi|Sunzi]] ("[[wikisource:The_Art_of_War#I._LAYING_PLANS|Laying Plans, Number 24]]")
Literally: Attack him where he is unprepared, appear where you are not expected.
===Idiom===
'''[[攻]][[其]][[无]][[备]]，[[出]][[其]][[不]][[意]]'''
# catch somebody unawares
===Alternative forms===
[[攻其無備，出其不意]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
